---
title: Steaks and Easy Scalloped Potatoes with Herby Mushrooms and Green Beans
description: Hearty steak and our creamy, dreamy scalloped potatoes are guaranteed to make tonight's dinner extra special. We've simplified the potatoes by cutting them into rounds and pre-boiling them in sauce – no mandolines or long baking times required!
